    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Architectural order similar to the Ionic order, but differing in that the capital features a palmette motif rising between the two outer volutes, rather than being linked horizontally by a form at the top of the capital. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000096524/Betancourt, Aeolic Style in Architecture (1977)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Architectuurorde die lijkt op de Ionische order, maar afwijkt doordat het kapiteel een palmetmotief heeft tussen de twee buitenste voluten, en niet horizontaal aan de bovenkant verbonden is. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ordem arquitetônica semelhante à ordem jônica, mas diferindo pelo fato de o capitel apresentar um motivo de palmeta que se eleva entre as duas volutas externas, em vez de ser ligado horizontalmente por uma forma no topo do capitel. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109633/CVAA-BR Consortium (2020-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
